WHEELS IN THIS INDEX
--------------------
The following wheels were rebuilt for Windows x86_64 Python 3.12 by AMD TheRock
(guinmoon) and are redistributed here in accordance with their MIT license:

  - rocm (meta-package)
  - rocm-sdk-core
  - rocm-sdk-devel
  - rocm-sdk-libraries-gfx103x-all
  - torch (PyTorch 2.9.1 + ROCm support)
  - torchaudio (2.9.0 + ROCm support)
  - torchvision (0.24.0 + ROCm support)

AVAILABILITY & SUPPORT
----------------------
These wheels are provided as-is on a best-effort basis. PHATT TECH does not
guarantee continuous availability of this index. For production use, refer to
the official AMD ROCm wheels or build from source.

